---
import PageLayout from "../../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout
  title="Start Tonight | Ævyndal"
  description="A runnable starting location with problems, pressures, and immediate hooks."
>
  <header class="pageHead">
    <h1>Start Tonight</h1>
    <p>Pick a location. Present the problem. Let the world push back.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>How to Use This Page</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Choose one starting location</li>
      <li>Read only the bold text</li>
      <li>Start play within 10 minutes</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Default Starting Location</h2>
    <p><strong>Vireskya</strong> is a frontier village on contested land.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Immediate problem:</strong> something valuable went missing last night</li>
      <li><strong>Pressure:</strong> blame is spreading faster than facts</li>
      <li><strong>Complication:</strong> two factions want incompatible outcomes</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>NPCs in Motion</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>The Elder:</strong> wants order restored before outsiders intervene</li>
      <li><strong>The Scout:</strong> knows more than they admit</li>
      <li><strong>The Third Party:</strong> benefits if violence escalates</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>If the Players Stall</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>An accusation turns public</li>
      <li>A body is found</li>
      <li>The valuable item resurfaces in the wrong hands</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Next Steps</h2>
    <p>
      When consequences start to land, move to
      <a href="/resources/">GM Tools</a>
      to escalate pressure and track fallout.
    </p>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
